# 🚗 Voice-Controlled Smart Car

A Bluetooth-based voice-controlled car developed using Arduino UNO and the BT Voice Control for Arduino app. The car responds to voice commands like "forward", "backward", "left", "right", and "stop" through a Bluetooth connection.

---

## 📌 Features

- Control car movement via voice commands
- Bluetooth connectivity using HC-05 module
- Simple Arduino-based circuit design
- Real-time command execution
- Supports basic directional commands

---

## 📷 Components Used

- Arduino UNO  
- HC-05 Bluetooth Module  
- L298N Motor Driver Module  
- DC Motors (x2 or x4)  
- 9V Battery  
- Chassis  
- Connecting wires  

---

## 📱 Voice Commands (through BT Voice Control app)

- `Forward`
- `Backward`
- `Left`
- `Right`
- `Stop`

