---

## 📝 How to Run

1. Connect the components as per the circuit diagram.
2. Upload the Arduino code (`Voice_Controlled_Car.ino`) to the Arduino UNO.
3. Pair your phone with the HC-05 Bluetooth module.
4. Open the "BT Voice Control for Arduino" app.
5. Connect to the paired HC-05 module.
6. Send voice commands to control the car.

